             was indicted for <rs id="t18220220-83-off439" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18220220-83-off439" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18220220-83-off439" type="offenceSubcategory" value="pocketpicking"></interp>
               stealing. on the <rs id="t18220220-83-cd440" type="crimeDate">20th of February</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18220220-83-off439 t18220220-83-cd440"></join>, one handkerchief, value 4 s., the goods of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18220220-83-victim891" type="victimName">
                           Owen 
                           Edwards
                        <interp inst="t18220220-83-victim891" type="surname" value="Edwards"></interp>
